      "text": "3) Un guardia varias siestas intervalos similares\n(1518-11-01 00:00) Guard #10 begins shift\n(1518-11-01 00:01) falls asleep\n(1518-11-01 00:50) wakes up\n(1518-11-02 00:00) Guard #99 begins shift\n(1518-11-02 00:20) falls asleep\n(1518-11-02 00:22) wakes up\n(1518-11-03 00:00) Guard #99 begins shift\n(1518-11-03 00:20) falls asleep\n(1518-11-03 00:22) wakes up\n(1518-11-04 00:00) Guard #99 begins shift\n(1518-11-04 00:20) falls asleep\n(1518-11-04 00:22) wakes up\n\nnaps: {10: [(1, 49)], 99: [(20, 21), (20, 21), (20, 21)]}\n  Guard 10: 50 min totales, todos freq 1\n  Guard 99: 6 min totales, min 20 y 21 tienen freq 3\n  Guard 99 gana porque tiene la mayor frecuencia en un solo minuto (3 > 1)\n\nguard = 99, minute = 20\n99 * 20 = 1980",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "3) Un guardia varias siestas intervalos similares\n(1518-11-01 00:00) Guard #10 begins shift\n(1518-11-01 00:01) falls asleep\n(1518-11-01 00:50) wakes up\n(1518-11-02 00:00) Guard #99 begins shift\n(1518-11-02 00:20) falls asleep\n(1518-11-02 00:22) wakes up\n(1518-11-03 00:00) Guard #99 begins shift\n(1518-11-03 00:20) falls asleep\n(1518-11-03 00:22) wakes up\n(1518-11-04 00:00) Guard #99 begins shift\n(1518-11-04 00:20) falls asleep\n(1518-11-04 00:22) wakes up\n\nnaps: {10: [(1, 49)], 99: [(20, 21), (20, 21), (20, 21)]}\n  Guard 10: 50 min totales, todos freq 1\n  Guard 99: 6 min totales, min 20 y 21 tienen freq 3\n  Guard 99 gana porque tiene la mayor frecuencia en un solo minuto (3 > 1)\n\nguard = 99, minute = 20\n99 * 20 = 1980",
      "autoResize": true,
